high_descs: Move to stand in front of the dishwasher and microwave.
Pick up the sharp knife from the counter.
Carry the knife to the fridge.
Open the fridge and use the knife to slice the potato on the top shelf.
Carry the knife to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the knife inside.
Move back to the fridge.
Open the fridge and remove a slice of potato.
Carry the slice of potato to the microwave.
Place the slice of potato in the microwave, turn it on, and then remove the potato once heated.
Carry the potato slice to the green trash bin in the corner.
Place the potato slice in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a heated slice of potato.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter above the dishwasher.
Pick up the yellow knife behind the spatula on the counter.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Cut up the potato closest to you in the fridge then close the fridge.
Turn left and walk to the microwave.
Place the knife behind the green cup in the microwave.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Pick up a piece of the potato from the fridge.
Turn left and walk to the microwave.
Microwave the piece of potato and then pick up the piece of potato from the microwave and close the microwave.
Turn around and walk to the green trash can in the corner.
Place the piece of potato into the green trash can.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved piece of potato into the green trash can.

high_descs: Turn and face the counter to the left of the microwave.
Pick the knife up from the counter.
Move to the right and turn to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and slice the potato on the shelf.
Move left to face the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave on the counter.
Move to the right and turn to face the fridge.
Take a slice of potato from the fridge.
Go to the left and face the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave and turn it on and then take the potato out of the microwave.
Cross the room and stand to face the trash can.
Put the potato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in the trash.
